node.text:
Another one of my projects that my husband revealed that he actually didn’t know what I was talking about when I described what I was doing in here... but he just lets me get on with it anyway! 

All the details are in an IGTV and the links to everything I used is in my highlights

NB the paint is self priming & self sealing. If your paint isn’t then you will need to use a separate primer & a separate sealer 

Credit: @lucys_hillside_house
